                '$_counter',
                style: Theme.of(context).textTheme.headlineMedium!.copyWith(color: Colors.white),
              ),
              SizedBox(
                height: 60,
                width: 200,
                child: CustomButton(
                  minWidth: 200,
                  label: 'Increment',
                  onPress: () => _incrementCounter(),
                ),
              ),
              const SizedBox(height: 20),
              const Text(
                'Â© 2024 Bajaj Auto Credit Ltd. All Rights Reserved.',
                style: TextStyle(
                  color: Colors.white,
                  fontSize: 12,
                  fontWeight: FontWeight.w400,
